news.title: Waymo pauses robotaxi service in San Francisco after blackout chaos — Musk says Tesla car service unaffected
news.description: As power outages spread Saturday, videos shared on social media appeared to show multiple Waymo vehicles stalled in traffic in different parts of San Francisco.

news.title: Epstein files: A number of documents, including Trump photo, reportedly removed from DOJ release site
news.description: A missing photo shows a desk displaying a large assortment of framed pictures and other items. Among them is a picture showing President Donald Trump's face.

news.title: Disney's 'Avatar: Fire and Ash' disappoints with weak $88 million domestic opening
news.description: Disney's "Avatar: Fire and Ash" tallied just $88 million during its domestic debut, well shy of the $110 million to $125 million range analysts had expected.
